"tid":1561344,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"9015bb0bebd43e6482b60728e2c1ab8f53441f3b","tid":1561344,"uid":245670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789f93cdb0936d6bf1cbda975f614667742eb70e","tid":1561344,"uid":82536,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9015bb0bebd43e6482b60728e2c1ab8f53441f3b","tid":1561344,"uid":245670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:38:02.000Z","msg":"好啦咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係「愛滋藥」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n絕對唔係有歧視 但touch wood 比人捉左去新屋嶺<br />\n叫天不應 叫地不聞<br />\n只可以諗各樣方法保護自己<br />\n<br />\n如果你有「愛滋藥」（未必要真藥）<br />\n+ 手機好多有關控制病情既folder / 手機lock screen 已經係有關既圖<br />\n<br />\n佢又無得fc 你係咪真係有<br />\n至少可以阻嚇到d 垃圾姦女義士<br />\n男義士比人打到流曬血 一行近就噴血or 噴口水<br />\n顏射落佢面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再行近就再噴 <br />\n<br />\n佢唔信就再補d 數據佢聽<br />\n&quot;至2018年年底，中國大陸存活愛滋病感染者約125萬&quot;<br />\n&quot;香港 自1984年以來，累積發現8,053人受愛滋病病毒感染&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔清楚入面咩情況 做唔做到咁理想真係唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望拋磚引玉 大家再諗下有咩保護自己既方法"},{"pid":"642fa080268f3cbb7bdbe52dda1eb6f5ebe35aee","tid":1561344,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"46157d33da7353b87e54af4510d3cef9fd8bdb4c","tid":1561344,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"e183819f601c307a91684fa6ff6849f4697c5342","tid":1561344,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime